          "default_html" : "<p><span style=\"font-size: 30px; color: #4698cb; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Dear&nbsp;{{contact.firstname}},</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Congratulations and welcome to Reposit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Congratulations and welcome to Reposit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #4698cb; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Heading Level 2</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Congratulations and welcome to Reposit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This is a bullet style</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This is a bullet style ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Congratulations and welcome to Reposit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This is a step style</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This is a step style ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This is a step style ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt.</span></li>\n</ol>",
          "html" : "<p><span style=\"font-size: 30px; color: #4698cb; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Dear&nbsp;{{ contact.firstname }},</span></p>\n<p>We all have someone we go to for advice, knowing our friends and peers will always give us an honest opinion.<br><br>So with a big appreciative smile, I'm reaching out to ask if you would be one of those trusted people and share your positive story on a few review sites - or even just give us a quick score!<br><br>Below are a few links to make life a little easier:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Product review</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.productreview.com.au/write-review\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.productreview.com.au/write-review</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Facebook</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RepositPower\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.facebook.com/RepositPower</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Visit the Reposit Facebook page.<br>Select the More tab, then reviews and type away!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Google</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Search for \"Reposit Power\" on Google</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">On the right-hand side of the search page our Google business details will appear, click write a review and leave your story.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Thank you for your ongoing support.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://f.hubspotusercontent40.net/hubfs/3445699/email%20contact%20row%20-%20mark%20and%20annette.jpg\" alt=\"email contact row - mark and annette\" style=\"width: 600px; max-width: 600px;\" width=\"600\"></p>"
